text-node.description:
Deletes old custom objects identified by their name and their maximum object age.
Task Configuration Example:
{  "pipeline" : "MiscJobs-DeleteOldCustomObjects",  "name" : "DeleteOldCustomObjects",  "customObjectIDs" : ["SiteJobStatus", "JobStatus"],  "maxObjectAge" : 15 }

Deletes old files identified by the base folder, the information if recursive search should be allowed and their maximum file age.
Task Configuration Example:
{  "pipeline" : "MiscJobs-DeleteOldFiles",  "name" : "Cleanup Impex Logs",  "folder" : "/IMPEX/log",  "recursive" : true, "deleteEmptyFolders" : true, "maxAge" : 10 }

Invalidates the web cache on different level
Task Configuration Example:
{"name" : "Invalidate Web Cache",  "pipeline" : "MiscJobs-InvalidateWebCache", "static" : false, "page" : true, "site" : true }

Updates the search indexes according to the task configuration.
Task Configuration Example:
{"name" : "Update Product Search Indexes",  "pipeline" : "MiscJobs-UpdateProductSearchIndexes", "index" : "content", "incremental" : true, "currentSite" : true }
